Company Overview
The Dreyfus Sustainable U.S. Equity Portfolio, Inc. is an open ended variable annuity equity mutual fund launched and managed by The Dreyfus Corporation. The fund is co-managed by Newton Investment Management (North America) Limited. It invests in public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in socially conscious stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations, with market capitalizations of $5 billion or more. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis by focusing on factors like environmental analysis, which includes an assessment of material environmental is...
The Dreyfus Sustainable U.S. Equity Portfolio, Inc. is an open ended variable annuity equity mutual fund launched and managed by The Dreyfus Corporation. The fund is co-managed by Newton Investment Management (North America) Limited. It invests in public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in socially conscious stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations, with market capitalizations of $5 billion or more. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis by focusing on factors like environmental analysis, which includes an assessment of material environmental issues, social analysis, which includes an assessment of material social issues, and governance analysis, which includes an assessment of corporate governance structures and processes to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. The fund does not seek to invest in stocks of companies involved in the manufacture of tobacco products. It employs proprietary research to create its portfolio. The fund was formerly known as The Dreyfus Socially Responsible Growth Fund, Inc. The Dreyfus Sustainable U.S. Equity Portfolio, Inc. was formed on October 7, 1993 and is domiciled in the United States.
