The Dreyfus Sustainable U.S. Equity Portfolio, Inc. Key Developments

The Dreyfus Socially Responsible Growth Fund, Inc., Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Mar 09, 2017
Jan 10 17
The Dreyfus Socially Responsible Growth Fund, Inc., Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Mar 09, 2017, at 09:30 US Eastern Standard Time. Location: 200 Park Avenue 7th Floor New York, NY 10166 United States Agenda: To approve removing the fund's current fundamental social investment policy and related fundamental social considerations regarding its investment strategy; to approve a sub-investment advisory agreement between Dreyfus and Newton Investment Management (North America) Limited with respect to the fund; to approve changing the fund's investment objective; to approve the implementation of a ‘manager of managers’ arrangement; to approve changing a fundamental investment restriction; and to transact such other business as may properly come before the meeting, or any adjournments thereof.


